cast.name: 奥利维亚·杰森 Olivia Jewson
皮特·麦克佛森 Peter McPherson

introduction: Silence can't always hide feelings. Talented Molly earns a scholarship to a prestigious performing arts school, but feels socially awkward as her dysfunctional home life in urban London differs hugely from her peer group, and a maelstrom of cyber bullying, physical and verbal bullying together with jostling egos and puzzling sexual tensions pushes her into a spiral of self sabotage. Will any so called friend be there when she is tipped over the edge?
